🎓 GP Nanakpur College - Official Website Redesign
HTML5CSS3JavaScript

A modern, responsive website design for Government Polytechnic Nanakpur.

🌐 Live Project
Original Website: https://gpnanakpur.ac.in/

This project is a redesigned concept to improve the UI/UX and user experience for the college.

📝 About The Project
This is a fully responsive landing page created using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. The main purpose of this project is to provide a clean, modern, and fast interface for students and staff.

It includes sections for:

Hero Section with quick stats
Academic Programs (Tabs)
Campus Life & Infrastructure
Latest News & Events
Contact Form
✨ Features
Responsive Design: Works perfectly on mobile, tablet, and desktop.
Modern UI: Dark theme with smooth animations and gradient effects.
Interactive Tabs: Programs section updates dynamically using JavaScript.
Fast Loading: Pure HTML/CSS/JS with no heavy frameworks.
🚀 How to Run
Clone the repository:
git clone https://github.com/your-username/your-repo-name.git
Open index.html:Just double-click the index.html file to view it in your browser.
